{"tid":1636132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個人小小見解 趁未區選之前先發制人","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:07:48.000Z","uid":90838,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af17e13debf308f4d324fe5967087aca35e6016f","tid":1636132,"uid":90838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"11月區選<br />\n傻既都知建制會係呢次到玩撚完<br />\n咁應該點做呢 緊係用緊急法阻止選舉啦<br />\n有咩藉口？就會話手足日日裝修 搞到香港好撚危險<br />\n所以選舉果日會好撚危險 都係推遲/原班人馬續任算了<br />\n有咩方法阻止狗府咁做？我唔知work唔work但可以試下民間記者會宣讀聲明/眾籌登晒全港甚至世界各地既頭條/保證手足果日絕對唔會亂郁<br />\n點解咁早做定？香港人係好第一印象 如果呢個focus 比狗府搶撚左先 塑造暴徒形象 咁就真係唔洗選都似<br />\n所以最好就盡快先發制人<br />\n到時狗府有藉口既話 大家又可以拎正牌裝修師傅上身了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎大家交流分享睇法<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n狗同政府一定會有一日係被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28ef3ea8111a4f6a1806f706f69de196784fab2","tid":1636132,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"「緊急」要草船借箭！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d578fbc5ea29be098314e94a4a12270b6820f4c9","tid":1636132,"uid":90838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"48bf9fa443282fe4b0860c24a35f458c11871499","tid":1636132,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:48:39.000Z","msg":"請幫手推爆黑警散布謠言!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［極醜惡又一例證］香港警察又掩埋真相 鼓吹謠言散播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636039</a>"},{"pid":"88dfe78851e6574d63d2ebb2d17b8a90ca270028","tid":1636132,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:49:41.000Z","ms